===Etymology===
From {{inh|pl|sla-pro|*věža}}. Cognates include Slovene {{term|veža||hallway|lang=sl}}, Russian {{term|вежа||caravan; tower|lang=ru}}, Slovak {{term|veža||tower|lang=sk}}.

===Pronunciation===
